
Q-1 Below are the explanation k-means algorithms with R.

Kmeans:-
Here we know the number of clusters in which we want to devide the dataset. For each cluster intially select the random centroid 
and then consider it as mean. Each point assgined mean using nearest neighbour method.

This is repetative process and repeats untill we get centres doesnt mvoe anymore.

